<h2>Usage</h2>
<p>A section provides a selection of background colour and style options to help you build and design.</p>
<p>Do's:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Use it with or without a container.</li>
  <li>Use it inside the grid.</li>
  <li>Organise a group of components together that provide functionality for the
    user.
  </li>
</ul>
