<h3>Inverted colours</h3>
<p>To use components and links within sections with a dark or supplementary background, use the <code>nsw-section--invert</code> class. Because supplementary backgrounds must have enough contrast with white text (#FFFFFF), Green 02, Orange 02, Yellow 02, and Brown 02 cannot be used in an inverted section. See <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="/docs/content/design/theming.html#corporate" aria-label="Open the theming guidance page (opens in a new tab)">Theming</a> for the complete list of compliant colours.</p>
{{#>_docs-example separated="true"}}
<section class="nsw-section nsw-section--brand-dark nsw-section--invert">
  <!-- START: Section content -->
  <div class="nsw-container">
    {{>_accordion model.accordion-1 type="details"}}
  </div>
</section>
{{/_docs-example}}
